ectors exhibit a W-extended symmetry but the ell/2\neven sectors do not. Moreover, the naive trace summing over all ell even\nsectors does not yield a modular invariant.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 23 Oct 2009 06:12:19 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 8 Jan 2010 06:33:21 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 26 Feb 2010 00:21:40 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-03-13"}
