in modulation. Remarkably, by further decreasing temperature,\na relatively narrow feature emerges from the broad IC NMR signal, manifesting\nthe formation of a solitonic modulation as T->0.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 23 Oct 2009 12:20:39 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-14"}
